# ADAS Edge — Device Target Tiers

Reference for the QNN object-detection pipeline. Covers the dev target (S22+) and
the deployment candidates (S26 family). The pipeline is identical across all of
them — only the **HTP architecture string**, **SoC platform id**, and **thermal
envelope** change. Parameterize the QNN config on `TARGET_DEVICE`; everything else
(YOLO11n → ONNX → QNN → INT8 → benchmark) stays the same.

---

